1
00:00:07,600 --> 00:00:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Step right up and have a look...</font>

2
00:00:10,480 --> 00:00:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time for Yamishibai.</font>

3
00:00:10,610 --> 00:00:17,530
<font face="Times New Roman" size="44" color="#593826"><b>{\an8}<font color="#5e3623"><font color="#5c352c">Theatre of Darkness: Yamishibai</font></font></b></font>

4
00:00:13,360 --> 00:00:17,530
<font face="Times New Roman" size="22" color="#3d2b20"><font color="#2b1f0a">Musubime-sama</font></font>

5
00:00:17,080 --> 00:00:23,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the story of a young man and 
woman who recently started dating...</font>

6
00:00:23,360 --> 00:00:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I appreciate you always giving me a lift.</font>

7
00:00:27,340 --> 00:00:29,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When are you going to 
get your license, Toma?</font>

8
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:31,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's on the agenda.</font>

9
00:00:31,670 --> 00:00:34,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I heard something from 
my senpai at work today.</font>

10
00:00:34,880 --> 00:00:37,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You ever hear of Musubime-sama, 
the Sewn Eye Woman?</font>

11
00:00:37,120 --> 00:00:40,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure have. Yukari said 
she tried it before.</font>

12
00:00:40,130 --> 00:00:40,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?</font>

13
00:00:42,010 --> 00:00:43,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I remember right...</font>

14
00:00:44,690 --> 00:00:48,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you're supposed to go to a big 
shrine in the mountains alone</font>

15
00:00:48,280 --> 00:00:50,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">on the night of a new moon.</font>

16
00:00:50,220 --> 00:00:52,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As the time passes, eventually...</font>

17
00:00:55,480 --> 00:00:57,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Musubime-sama will appear.</font>

18
00:00:59,170 --> 00:01:03,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ritual with her needs to be 
carried out with utmost respect.</font>

19
00:01:04,460 --> 00:01:06,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You give her a polite introduction,</font>

20
00:01:06,480 --> 00:01:09,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and then the process begins 
with a specific order.</font>

21
00:01:09,700 --> 00:01:13,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Musubime-sama's hair is really kinked 
and tends to get caught on her comb.</font>

22
00:01:14,430 --> 00:01:18,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're not careful about how hard you 
go, you can end up pulling her hair out.</font>

23
00:01:19,840 --> 00:01:22,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If that happens, you need 
to beg for forgiveness.</font>

24
00:01:23,560 --> 00:01:27,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You cannot upset Musubime-sama, 
no matter what.</font>

25
00:01:27,030 --> 00:01:30,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you do, your wish won't come true.</font>

26
00:01:31,350 --> 00:01:35,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And after she forgives you, 
you resume the ritual.</font>

27
00:01:36,730 --> 00:01:39,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once the combing is done, 
you put her hair up.</font>

28
00:01:42,830 --> 00:01:45,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After that, you give your 
regards one more time,</font>

29
00:01:46,740 --> 00:01:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and then, for the first time, 
you look at her face.</font>

30
00:01:52,720 --> 00:01:55,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You cannot recoil at the 
sight of how horrible it is.</font>

31
00:01:56,240 --> 00:01:58,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because the ritual still isn't over.</font>

32
00:01:59,120 --> 00:02:01,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Last comes the eye-opening.</font>

33
00:02:01,640 --> 00:02:05,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You have to be careful not 
to harm Musubime-sama.</font>

34
00:02:05,590 --> 00:02:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do that, and you won't leave alive.</font>

35
00:02:09,860 --> 00:02:14,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, once her eyes are open, 
you give your final regards.</font>

36
00:02:15,900 --> 00:02:19,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, once Musubime-sama's eyes are open,</font>

37
00:02:19,890 --> 00:02:22,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you're supposed to end up with 
the object of your affections.</font>

38
00:02:22,730 --> 00:02:24,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really know your stuff.</font>

39
00:02:24,630 --> 00:02:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No, Yukari just likes to talk.</font>

40
00:02:29,600 --> 00:02:33,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From what I heard, 
there's a continuation, though.</font>

41
00:02:33,460 --> 00:02:36,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is? I-I don't know about that.</font>

42
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:41,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, Musubime-sama 
needs to have eyes.</font>

43
00:02:41,060 --> 00:02:41,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eyes?</font>

44
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like, eyeballs.</font>

45
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:45,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, once her eyes are open,</font>

46
00:02:45,330 --> 00:02:48,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if the sockets are empty, 
you'll never end up with anyone.</font>

47
00:02:48,380 --> 00:02:49,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way!</font>

48
00:02:49,310 --> 00:02:51,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not lying. It's just what I heard.</font>

49
00:02:51,580 --> 00:02:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's... Then what I saw...</font>

50
00:02:54,510 --> 00:02:57,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It didn't mean I'd end up with you?</font>

51
00:02:58,470 --> 00:03:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you muttering about?</font>

52
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't see! I can't see!</font>

53
00:03:05,830 --> 00:03:06,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong?!</font>

54
00:03:06,580 --> 00:03:09,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't see! Why?! I can't see!</font>

55
00:03:11,150 --> 00:03:13,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't see! I can't see!</font>

56
00:03:26,180 --> 00:03:30,180
<font face="Times New Roman" size="44" color="#593826"><b>{\an8}<font size="34">Theatre of Darkness: Yamishibai</font></b></font>

57
00:03:26,850 --> 00:03:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The end.</font>

